import React, { Component } from 'react' import 'bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css' import './Quic.css' export default class Quick extends Component { state = { headcount: 0, proc: 1 } componentDidMount() { this.getHeadcount(); } getHeadcount(){ fetch('/headcount') .then(res => res.json()) .then(({ headcount, proc }) => this.setState({ headcount, proc })) } render() { return (
Headcount {this.state.proc}%

{this.state.headcount}

E. Headcount 6%

762

Productivity 3%

90%

E. Productivity 5%

110%

Availability 5%

88%

Shrinkage 5%

12%

) } }
